      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(K)$ et\n$U = \\begin{pmatrix} 1       &\\dots  &1       \\cr\n                \\vdots  &       &\\vdots  \\cr\n                1       &\\dots  &1       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(K)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(U = \\begin{pmatrix} 1       &amp;\\dots  &amp;1       \\cr\n                \\vdots  &amp;       &amp;\\vdots  \\cr\n                1       &amp;\\dots  &amp;1       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b1d32f31-e70d-45d0-8a11-1179d3b1b9ba",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Démontrer que :\n    $\\det(A + \\alpha U) = \\det A + \\alpha \\sum \\text{cofacteurs de } A$.",
        "html": "<p>Démontrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det(A + \\alpha U) = \\det A + \\alpha \\sum \\text{cofacteurs de } A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
