      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire la valeur de\n     $D(a,b,c) = \\begin{vmatrix}a       & b      & \\dots  & b      \\cr\n                           c       & \\ddots & \\ddots & \\vdots \\cr\n                           \\vdots  & \\ddots & \\ddots & b      \\cr\n                           c       & \\dots  & c      & a      \\end{vmatrix}$,\n  \\begin{enumerate}",
        "html": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e7f96f7a-c42b-49df-a818-ee3018a152b7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "\\begin{enumerate}",
        "html": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ed292eb2-5a6a-4fec-977f-633f1d4d6d66",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $b \\ne c$.",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(b \\ne c\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "77111354-e8f2-4fed-9952-51fcd2351bc3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\begin{cases} D(a-b,0,c-b) = (a-b)^n \\cr\n                       D(a-c,b-c,0) = (a-c)^n \\cr\\end{cases}  \\Rightarrow \n               D(a,b,c) = \\frac { c(a-b)^n - b(a-c)^n } {c-b}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{cases} D(a-b,0,c-b) = (a-b)^n \\cr\n                       D(a-c,b-c,0) = (a-c)^n \\cr\\end{cases}  \\Rightarrow \n               D(a,b,c) = \\frac { c(a-b)^n - b(a-c)^n } {c-b}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "71f7c3f7-8f8e-46f2-80ee-77994f633476",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $b = c$.",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(b = c\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "97df0de3-9bb1-4778-8b57-25f4c182bc17",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\det( (a-b)I + bU ) = (a-b)^n + nb(a-b)^{n-1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det( (a-b)I + bU ) = (a-b)^n + nb(a-b)^{n-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
